{"tid":1405984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班偽前線左膠又重掌大局，泛民班撚屌死性不改","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:00:21.000Z","uid":40250,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ccadf9f682084f0c523b00ef18ff4aac51abfe67","tid":1405984,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:07.000Z","msg":"組人鏈，一二一二後退，有民居但岩打既就話唔好開戰會傷到市民，無民居有差佬佈晒防，就話即管開戰，義士受傷被捕又可以借機cap水，示威者既安危？ WFC??<br />\n<br />\nBe water,  齊上齊落？<br />\n同差佬傾好圍捕就叫你守，有得打個陣就叫你be water,永遠敵進我退，唔會還擊。有手足俾差佬夾都拉你走, 叫你唔好理，邊撚到齊上齊落?<br />\n<br />\n每日搞場大龍鳳，嘥義士熱情精力時間金錢，就係幫泛民增曝光率，永遠只有示威者付出代價，義士受傷被捕？WFC? 你還擊打柒差佬, 即刻叫你唔好戀戰<br />\n<br />\n知點解永遠打得贏差佬個幾次都係班街坊?"},{"pid":"19b58782176ca9381a8fd115ed35da6b3b393876","tid":1405984,"uid":271280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:52:42.000Z","msg":"？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa